*  devices. Phys. Status Solidi A, 211: 21?26. doi:10.1002/pssa.201330197
* [Ste15] S. I. Stepanov, V. I. Nikolaev, V. E. Bougrov, and A. E. Romanov, Rev. Adv. Mater. Sci. 44, 63 (2016)
